props.name: signMask
props.desc: Extract the sign bits from each lane return them in the first 4 bits. "x" lane is bit 0. "y" lane is bit 1. "z" lane is bit 2. "w" lane is bit 3.

desc:
Float32x4 immutable value type and operations.

Float32x4 stores 4 32-bit floating point values in "lanes". The lanes are "x", "y", "z", and "w" respectively.
